nodes.text: The Lastdark Club was an exclusive club in Coronet City on Corellia. It was in the top floor of the world's tallest building, which was where it got its name: when the sun set, it was the last location to be in sunlight. Rostek Horn became a member in 8 ABY and supplied half the club's plant arrangements. Its decoration included nerf-hide chairs and it offered Corellian brandy.
